# --- Personal Account --- #
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User cupertinorp@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d $HOME/.config/mutt/accounts/personal/pass.gpg | awk 'NF>1{print $NF}'"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *

